a6%2581%25e6%25b1%2582%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%2594%25b9%25e6%25ad%25a3&h=f7a5d1ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20200511/s00001/1589136708567/%e8%bc%94%e8%ad%a6%e4%b8%80%e5%93%a5%e6%b6%89%e5%a4%a9%e5%8f%b0%e5%83%ad%e5%bb%ba%e9%9c%b8%e5%ae%98%e5%9c%b0-%e5%b1%8b%e7%bd%b2%e5%9c%b0%e7%bd%b2%e8%aa%bf%e6%9f%a5-%e6%a5%8a%e7%a5%96%e8%b3%9c-%e5%80%98%e4%b8%8d%e7%ac%a6%e8%a6%81%e6%b1%82%e6%9c%83%e6%94%b9%e6%ad%a3</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】再有警方高層涉嫌僭建<strong>。本報接獲投訴，指稱現任香港輔助警察隊總監兼新鴻基地產市務總監楊祖賜，其位於西貢北港新村的村屋涉僭建，在天台加建面積約天台一半、頂鋪太陽能板的構築物；並涉嫌擴展村屋地段，佔用官地泊車。有關注團體指出，該構築物已圍封，違反屋宇署規定。</strong>楊祖賜回覆本報稱，該構築物並非固定建築物，是以可裝拆式圍板搭建，已委託專業測量師跟進，「如果真有什麼是不符要求，就會改正，或拆除某些不符要求的地方」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200511/s00006/ff456d44ddb0b7b99e6f9a67109c97d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200511%2Fs00006%2Fff456d44ddb0b7b99e6f9a67109c97d6.jpg&h=8f4458ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fea26d454ed985d4f5e72474353312cb34520c41","tid":2011221,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:23:08.000Z","msg":"明報記者識用Google Streetview<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec62ae196b001300d0bdc59d5c744c7bc769ba28","tid":2011221,"uid":117282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:25:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d932cf29ca5a2e635e30c22f5f68298aa8415bce","tid":2011221,"uid":98431,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:26:32.000Z","msg":"知法犯法 全是狗賊"},{"pid":"762b8dc294023a725ab3be79b48247f002f4c3a5","tid":2011221,"uid":51271,"like":6,"disl